'''Izimay''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: ''''''') d [[aburɣes]] yeṭṭafaren [[tafesna (tasnudert)|tafesna]] n [[Ephemeroptera]] (seg [[Tagrikt|tegrikt]] '''εφημερος''' - ephemeros = "tudert gezzilen" + '''πτερος''' - pteron = afriw), dɣa tettusesmel deg tegrawt n [[Timzifriwin|temzifriwin]] igebren daɣen seg  [[tatlulleɣt]] yakk d [[taẓewt n tala]] igan d [[ibureɣsen n waman]] deg tallit ur newwi ara (anda tettwasemma "[[tamragt]]"), tettidir yiwen n useggas deg waman iẓidanen. Ma d aburɣes amawaṭ yettidir seg kra n tesdatin alamma d kra n wussan s unect n [[talmest|telmest]].<br/>
Ar ass-a, llant wazal n 2,500 n telmas yettwassnen deg umadal, gar-asent 630 n telmas ttidirent deg [[Tamrikt n Ugafa|temrikt tagafant]].

